WEBVTT

00:08.309 --> 00:09.842
My mom's having an affair.

00:09.844 --> 00:11.677
- Farrah, open up!
- Dad?

00:11.679 --> 00:13.312
- What's the answer?
- I haven't had any answers

00:13.314 --> 00:14.546
Since you slept
with my best friend.

00:14.548 --> 00:17.316
- There it is, your trump card.
- I have to go.

00:17.318 --> 00:19.718
- I'm not impressive enough?
- You're in high school.

00:19.720 --> 00:21.754
God, if i'd known
it was gonna be like this,

00:21.756 --> 00:22.755
I never would have
outed you.

00:22.757 --> 00:24.823
Hello, karma.
Please, get in.

00:24.825 --> 00:26.725
I know what i want.

00:29.597 --> 00:31.196
[ticking]

00:31.198 --> 00:32.631
Welcome to detention.

00:32.633 --> 00:35.567
For the next seven hours,
you belong to me.

00:35.569 --> 00:37.936
You will sit in your seats
quietly

00:37.938 --> 00:38.904
Without your cell phones.

00:38.906 --> 00:40.739
No texting.
No candy crushing.

00:40.741 --> 00:42.941
No snapchatting your genitalia.

00:42.943 --> 00:46.412
Instead, you will silently
ruminate over the shortcomings

00:46.414 --> 00:48.580
That have landed you here.
Dig deep.

00:48.582 --> 00:51.650
Figure out how not to repeat
the same mistake twice

00:51.652 --> 00:55.754
Or you could get your ged
and become an uber driver.

00:55.756 --> 00:58.891
[lively music]

00:58.893 --> 01:01.493
♪ ♪

01:03.000 --> 01:09.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:14.909 --> 01:16.775
Aren't you guys
all friends?

01:16.777 --> 01:20.679
Did you have a hot tub party
that got a little bit too real?

01:20.681 --> 01:24.516
I know shane's here
because of his naked protest,

01:24.518 --> 01:25.951
But what did the rest of you do?

01:25.953 --> 01:27.553
Clearly,
there was a clerical error.

01:27.555 --> 01:29.688
I'm sure
i'll be exonerated shortly.

01:29.690 --> 01:31.457
Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah.
Everybody's innocent.

01:31.459 --> 01:33.892
- [laughs]
- well, what about you, amy?

01:33.894 --> 01:35.360
[playful music]

01:35.362 --> 01:38.831
You obviously have never
watched <i> orange is the new black.</i>

01:38.833 --> 01:42.801
You don't ask someone
why they're doing time.

01:42.803 --> 01:43.769
And if you must know,

01:43.771 --> 01:47.539
I cut class because i was
watching a french new wave film

01:47.541 --> 01:49.575
At the austin film society.

01:49.577 --> 01:51.543
I thought you said
it was german.

01:51.545 --> 01:54.646
Yeah, right...
[laughs]

01:54.648 --> 01:56.715
It--it was german.

01:56.717 --> 01:57.883
<i>Danke schoen.</i>

01:57.885 --> 02:00.419
- What about you, karma?
- Yeah, did you and liam

02:00.421 --> 02:02.621
Finally get caught
having sex at school?

02:02.623 --> 02:04.623
- No.
- No.

02:04.625 --> 02:08.327
I fell asleep during geometry.

02:11.432 --> 02:12.364
What about you, liam?

02:12.366 --> 02:15.400
I took a conference call
during philosophy.

02:15.402 --> 02:17.169
What?
It was with our dubai office.

02:17.171 --> 02:18.904
It's really hard to coordinate
with the time difference.

02:18.906 --> 02:21.473
Oh, did you follow it up
with a round of golf

02:21.475 --> 02:23.408
And spot of day trading?

02:23.410 --> 02:24.476
What about you, felix?

02:24.478 --> 02:27.479
Let's just say that
turner has it out for me.

02:27.481 --> 02:28.514
Is it hot in here,

02:28.516 --> 02:29.448
Or is it just me?

02:29.450 --> 02:33.418
Turner doesn't turn the ac
on on saturdays.

02:33.420 --> 02:33.952
[sighs]

02:33.954 --> 02:35.988
Lauren, aren't you hot?

02:35.990 --> 02:36.989
I naturally run cold.

02:36.991 --> 02:38.857
- Like most reptil--
- finish that sentence,

02:38.859 --> 02:42.728
And i will stab you
with this pencil.

02:42.730 --> 02:46.365
[ticking]

02:52.873 --> 02:54.907
So, what's the deal
with you and liam?

02:54.909 --> 02:56.608
You two still not talking?

02:56.610 --> 02:59.611
[sighs]
not since l.A.

02:59.613 --> 03:02.714
Any new developments
in farrahgate?

03:02.716 --> 03:03.615
Um...Sort of.

03:03.617 --> 03:06.552
My mom promised that the fling
was totally over.

03:06.554 --> 03:07.819
Good. The last thing
you need

03:07.821 --> 03:11.623
Is farrah leaving bruce
for some new rando.

03:11.625 --> 03:13.659
Yeah, that would suck.

03:13.661 --> 03:14.893
Has lauren agreed
not to tell bruce?

03:14.895 --> 03:18.197
Not yet. He comes back
from a business trip tonight,

03:18.199 --> 03:19.698
And i don't know
what she's gonna do.

03:19.700 --> 03:22.601
You could ask her.
She's right behind you.

03:22.603 --> 03:25.737
[tense music]

03:25.739 --> 03:27.139
♪ ♪

03:27.141 --> 03:28.207
Hey, step-sis.

03:28.209 --> 03:30.209
Can we not talk about it?
I'm not in the mood.

03:30.211 --> 03:31.910
If you're still on the fence
about telling your dad,

03:31.912 --> 03:33.812
I highly recommend
not telling.

03:33.814 --> 03:35.781
I don't get why
you're covering for farrah.

03:35.783 --> 03:37.783
If i tell daddy,
they'll break up,

03:37.785 --> 03:38.684
And then she and your dad

03:38.686 --> 03:40.619
- Can get back together.
- Shh!

03:40.621 --> 03:42.921
And i don't want them
to get back together.

03:42.923 --> 03:46.592
All they do is fight.
They're like oil and vinegar.

03:46.594 --> 03:47.626
Oil and vinegar
are delicious.

03:47.628 --> 03:49.661
- You know what i mean.
- If you must know,

03:49.663 --> 03:51.797
I've decided i am
telling daddy.

03:51.799 --> 03:53.498
He's the innocent
victim here.

03:53.500 --> 03:55.500
But you'll be
splitting our family up.

03:55.502 --> 03:59.771
No, your mother
took care of that.

04:03.677 --> 04:05.911
Hey, buddy.

04:05.913 --> 04:08.146
How you doing?

04:08.148 --> 04:08.914
Fine.

04:08.916 --> 04:11.083
You can't keep
eating yourself up.

04:11.085 --> 04:13.685
Look, i know
you're depressed about duke.

04:13.687 --> 04:14.953
I'm eating
because i'm liberated.

04:14.955 --> 04:16.988
No more duke hovering
over my shoulder

04:16.991 --> 04:18.257
Shouting,
"lean and green."

04:18.259 --> 04:21.892
So you're telling me
you're happy you two broke up?

04:21.894 --> 04:22.995
Sure i'm sad he's gone,

04:22.997 --> 04:25.530
But if he can't see that i
did him a favor by outing him,

04:25.532 --> 04:27.532
That's his problem.

04:27.534 --> 04:28.734
[door opens]

04:28.736 --> 04:30.035
[booing and hissing]

04:30.037 --> 04:31.270
What the hell
are you doing here?

04:31.272 --> 04:34.106
Yeah, did you get lost
on the way to the donut shop?

04:34.108 --> 04:35.674
Oh, and did you
bring any with you?

04:35.676 --> 04:38.610
I'm here to escort lauren
to principal turner's office.

04:38.612 --> 04:39.811
I knew it.

04:39.813 --> 04:41.046
I'm exonerated.

04:41.048 --> 04:44.650
See you deviants on monday.

04:44.985 --> 04:47.519
Out of my way, narc.

04:49.790 --> 04:50.856
Okay, i'm dying to know.

04:50.858 --> 04:52.924
Why would your dad
put you in detention?

04:52.926 --> 04:56.194
Because he doesn't trust me
to be alone all day.

04:56.196 --> 04:58.630
Why?
All you do is play xbox.

04:58.632 --> 05:01.633
He has his reasons.

05:04.805 --> 05:06.104
Oh, come on!

05:06.106 --> 05:07.239
Just one.
I'm starving,

05:07.241 --> 05:09.741
And you've got
a 7-eleven over there.

05:09.743 --> 05:11.810
No, i need them all.

05:11.812 --> 05:13.145
Fine.

05:13.147 --> 05:16.048
Karma always has mints.

05:16.050 --> 05:19.184
[tense music]

05:19.186 --> 05:24.556
♪ ♪

05:24.558 --> 05:25.590
(karma)
what you doing?

05:25.592 --> 05:29.695
Uh, just looking
for a light refreshment.

05:29.697 --> 05:30.996
- Ooh, give me one.
- You know what?

05:30.998 --> 05:32.831
I really need to pee.
Come with me.

05:32.833 --> 05:34.266
Amy, i thought we got past

05:34.268 --> 05:35.600
Your fear of
peeing alone.

05:35.602 --> 05:38.537
It's not about that.
We need to talk, now.

05:38.539 --> 05:40.072
[both gasp]

05:40.074 --> 05:41.840
Lauren?

05:41.842 --> 05:43.842
You're not supposed
to be here.

05:43.844 --> 05:45.677
None of you are.
What is going on?

05:45.679 --> 05:48.113
They--they were sneaking out,
sir, but don't worry.

05:48.115 --> 05:49.114
I caught them.

05:49.116 --> 05:51.850
[lively music]

05:54.988 --> 05:57.189
Any further infractions
will be met with detention

05:57.191 --> 05:59.157
Until the end
of the school year.

05:59.159 --> 06:00.225
Are we clear?

06:00.227 --> 06:02.728
(all)
yes, sir.

06:05.232 --> 06:07.833
How could you take him back
after what he did to you?

06:07.835 --> 06:09.000
- What?
- Take who back?

06:09.002 --> 06:10.535
We caught lauren and theo
making out in the hallway.

06:10.537 --> 06:13.805
After amy and i
helped you out him?

06:13.807 --> 06:15.474
You outed theo too?

06:15.476 --> 06:16.608
Why am i not surprised?

06:16.610 --> 06:19.177
Lauren, he arrested my parents
and me and amy.

06:19.179 --> 06:20.879
Because he was
protecting our secret.

06:20.881 --> 06:22.881
Oh, lauren,
when are you gonna learn?

06:22.883 --> 06:24.015
Secrets always come out.

06:24.017 --> 06:25.250
Yeah, because you out them.

06:25.252 --> 06:29.788
Raise your hand if you've been
outed by shane harvey.

06:30.224 --> 06:33.492
- Thank you for your support.
- Oh, no, this isn't support.

06:33.494 --> 06:35.427
You've got a real problem
outing people.

06:35.429 --> 06:36.428
If you hadn't outed duke,

06:36.430 --> 06:37.963
You wouldn't be in this
situation right now,

06:37.965 --> 06:39.297
- So just admit it.
- I'll admit it

06:39.299 --> 06:40.599
If you admit
you're a corporate sellout

06:40.601 --> 06:42.267
And the whole artist thing
was a joke.

06:42.269 --> 06:44.102
Lauren,
you can't take him back.

06:44.104 --> 06:45.303
He's only gonna
hurt you again.

06:45.305 --> 06:46.505
I don't give a [bleep]
what you think.

06:46.507 --> 06:48.940
But you better keep it a secret
because if this comes out,

06:48.942 --> 06:50.609
- Theo loses his job.
- Fine.

06:50.611 --> 06:51.643
I'll keep your secret

06:51.645 --> 06:53.545
If you promise you
won't tell bruce that thing

06:53.547 --> 06:55.847
- I don't want you to tell him.
- What thing?

06:55.849 --> 06:59.284
The fact that your mom
is [bleep] your dad?

07:00.521 --> 07:03.622
That's who you caught your mom
with in the motel room?

07:03.624 --> 07:05.390
Why did you keep that
from me?

07:05.392 --> 07:06.992
We agreed no more secrets
between us.

07:06.994 --> 07:10.295
I know, but i knew that you
would be all mad and judgey

07:10.297 --> 07:11.329
Because you hate my dad.

07:11.331 --> 07:14.132
I hate how he blows in here
once in a blue moon

07:14.134 --> 07:15.367
If and when he pleases.

07:15.369 --> 07:16.435
He's a war journalist, karma.

07:16.437 --> 07:19.404
He doesn't exactly decide
when wars start or end.

07:19.406 --> 07:23.508
Wait, you didn't cut school
to see a film.

07:23.510 --> 07:24.543
You cut school to see him.

07:24.545 --> 07:27.312
Busted. I'm guilty
for spending time

07:27.314 --> 07:28.213
With my father.

07:28.215 --> 07:30.615
No, you're guilty
of yet another lie.

07:30.617 --> 07:32.517
Maybe we should all take
a deep breath.

07:32.519 --> 07:33.952
See, this is exactly
what happens

07:33.954 --> 07:35.454
When people aren't their true,
authentic self.

07:35.456 --> 07:37.923
Oh, enough with the
self-righteous bull[bleep].

07:37.925 --> 07:41.426
You act like you did duke
some huge favor by outing him,

07:41.428 --> 07:43.895
But you're guilt-eating
everything in this room

07:43.897 --> 07:45.197
That isn't made of plastic.

07:45.199 --> 07:46.531
You can't just do
the wrong thing

07:46.533 --> 07:49.067
And then pretend
it's for the right reason.

07:49.069 --> 07:51.002
Excellent point, booker.

07:51.004 --> 07:52.437
Keeping farrah's secret
is wrong,

07:52.439 --> 07:55.073
And claiming it's to keep
our family together

07:55.075 --> 07:56.141
Doesn't make it right.

07:56.143 --> 07:57.309
She swore
it didn't mean anything,

07:57.311 --> 07:59.144
So can we just forget about it
and move on?

07:59.146 --> 08:00.979
[laughs]
wow.

08:00.981 --> 08:02.514
Why does that
sound familiar?

08:02.516 --> 08:06.885
Oh, yeah, that's what you said
when you slept with liam.

08:06.887 --> 08:07.819
Like mother, like daughter.

08:07.821 --> 08:09.488
(lauren)
let's just sweep it
under the rug.

08:09.490 --> 08:11.623
I'm surprised there's any room
left under there.

08:11.625 --> 08:13.492
You're one
to talk about secrets.

08:13.494 --> 08:16.261
Okay, what's this?
Oh!

08:16.263 --> 08:20.465
It's a check
from max booker for $250,000.

08:20.467 --> 08:23.869
What's that about, karma?

08:25.105 --> 08:28.473
- What the hell is going on?
- That's a big check.

08:28.475 --> 08:33.044
But like, seriously,
that's twice the standard size.

08:33.046 --> 08:34.346
After we got back
from l.A.,

08:34.347 --> 08:38.383
Your father offered me that
check to stay away from you.

08:38.385 --> 08:40.619
- And you took it?
- No!

08:40.621 --> 08:43.288
Not yet.
I-i haven't cashed it.

08:43.289 --> 08:47.025
Yeah, but you haven't
torn it up either.

08:48.161 --> 08:53.265
Who wouldn't consider
taking $250,000?

08:53.267 --> 08:54.432
I've been such an idiot!

08:54.434 --> 08:56.268
It could help my parents
get back on their feet,

08:56.270 --> 08:57.769
Help pay for college.

08:57.771 --> 08:59.571
How could i not consider it
for even a second?

08:59.573 --> 09:01.706
After you left l.A.,
zita kissed me.

09:01.708 --> 09:04.109
She made it very clear
she wanted more,

09:04.111 --> 09:05.477
But i turned her down.

09:05.479 --> 09:07.412
It didn't take me a week
to think about it.

09:07.414 --> 09:09.247
Oh, yeah, well, too bad
you didn't think

09:09.249 --> 09:10.282
Before you slept with amy.

09:10.284 --> 09:11.917
- [sighs]
- karma, please leave me

09:11.919 --> 09:12.584
Out of it.

09:12.586 --> 09:13.518
Here we go again.

09:13.520 --> 09:15.520
You're taking a bribe
to stay away from me,

09:15.522 --> 09:17.188
But i'm the one
defending myself?

09:17.190 --> 09:20.458
I'm not rich, liam!
I didn't fall asleep in class

09:20.460 --> 09:21.860
Because i've been studying.

09:21.862 --> 09:24.462
I've been working
every catering gig i could get,

09:24.464 --> 09:27.332
And i live in
a freaking juice truck!

09:27.334 --> 09:29.367
It's so besides the point
it's not even funny.

09:29.369 --> 09:31.703
If you were offered that money
to stay away from amy,

09:31.705 --> 09:36.074
You wouldn't have
considered it for one second.

09:43.717 --> 09:46.084
[soft crying]

09:46.086 --> 09:49.387
Is he...Crying?

09:51.792 --> 09:54.059
You're right.

09:54.061 --> 09:57.095
I am a terrible person.

09:57.097 --> 09:58.196
I outed you two as lesbians

09:58.198 --> 10:02.133
Because i didn't want
lauren to win homecoming queen.

10:02.135 --> 10:07.305
And i outed your pills because
i wanted to take you down.

10:07.307 --> 10:10.075
And i outed duke because...

10:10.077 --> 10:11.610
I wanted to ruin his life.

10:11.612 --> 10:16.348
Instead,
he told me loved me.

10:16.350 --> 10:18.717
And now he hates me,

10:18.719 --> 10:21.686
And he should.

10:21.688 --> 10:23.421
I hate me.

10:23.423 --> 10:25.056
[somber music]

10:25.058 --> 10:26.591
Shane, man, come on.
Ease up.

10:26.593 --> 10:30.095
You did a bad thing, but that
doesn't make you a bad person.

10:30.097 --> 10:30.762
I've forgiven you,

10:30.764 --> 10:33.098
And what you did to me
was way worse.

10:33.100 --> 10:33.932
Have you told him

10:33.934 --> 10:35.800
- That you're sorry?
- It's too late.

10:35.802 --> 10:37.135
He leaves in,
like, an hour

10:37.137 --> 10:38.703
To train with
some famous muay thai fighter.

10:38.705 --> 10:40.405
Well,
then there's still time.

10:40.407 --> 10:42.641
We're breaking you
out of here.

10:42.643 --> 10:45.210
Ready to form voltron.

10:45.212 --> 10:47.245
[playful music]

10:47.247 --> 10:50.315
The '80s animated show?

10:50.317 --> 10:53.218
Nobody? Really?

10:59.626 --> 11:02.227
Okay, we have one hour
until he checks in again.

11:02.229 --> 11:04.362
But he locks the doors
on saturdays.

11:04.364 --> 11:05.764
Maybe we could get a key
somehow?

11:05.766 --> 11:07.332
- He's got it on his belt.
- Oh, what about

11:07.334 --> 11:08.900
The bathroom window?
It was open this morning.

11:08.902 --> 11:10.735
The bathroom window?
That thing is tiny.

11:10.737 --> 11:13.471
Regretting that jumbo bag
of cheesaritos?

11:13.473 --> 11:14.839
Let's roll.

11:14.841 --> 11:17.976
[lively music]

11:17.978 --> 11:19.844
♪ ♪

11:19.846 --> 11:21.312
[music stops]

11:21.314 --> 11:23.615
I did go running today...

11:23.617 --> 11:25.750
[tense music]

11:25.752 --> 11:27.886
How are we gonna
get by him?

11:27.888 --> 11:28.820
Pull the fire alarm.

11:28.822 --> 11:31.322
Shane can sneak out
in the chaos.

11:31.324 --> 11:32.657
- Neh--
- what?

11:32.659 --> 11:34.659
You and i
were about to get caught,

11:34.661 --> 11:35.794
So i created a distraction.

11:35.796 --> 11:39.164
Didn't know those things
spray permanent ink.

11:39.166 --> 11:41.066
That's how you got
detention!

11:41.068 --> 11:42.867
- I'll distract turner.
- How?

11:42.869 --> 11:45.570
I know what makes him tick.

11:45.572 --> 11:46.504
He's my dad.

11:46.506 --> 11:47.439
(all)
what?

11:47.441 --> 11:48.907
Yeah,
i don't exactly advertise it.

11:48.909 --> 11:52.811
It's not easy being the son
of the most hated man on campus.

11:52.813 --> 11:53.745
No, it's okay.

11:53.747 --> 11:56.915
What happens in detention
stays in detention.

11:56.917 --> 11:58.516
- Right?
- Right.

11:58.518 --> 11:59.684
- Right.
- Right.

11:59.686 --> 12:01.853
[playful music]

12:01.855 --> 12:03.722
Hey, dad?

12:03.724 --> 12:05.757
You never call me that
at school.

12:05.759 --> 12:06.891
What are you doing here?

12:06.893 --> 12:10.495
Uh...You remember when you
gave me the sex talk,

12:10.497 --> 12:12.430
And you said
if i had any questions,

12:12.432 --> 12:13.798
I could ask you anytime?

12:13.800 --> 12:15.834
Of course.

12:15.836 --> 12:17.435
Why do men have nipples?

12:17.437 --> 12:19.971
Well,
that's an excellent question.

12:19.973 --> 12:22.674
You see, not many
people realize this,

12:22.676 --> 12:25.877
But every embryo
begins developing as a female.

12:25.879 --> 12:28.480
[whispering]
we'll never make it in time.

12:28.482 --> 12:29.681
[engine starts]

12:29.683 --> 12:31.349
Handled.

12:31.351 --> 12:33.318
Book it, theo.

12:33.687 --> 12:36.955
And that's why masturbation
is perfectly healthy.

12:37.791 --> 12:39.924
- What a relief.
- Good.

12:39.926 --> 12:41.593
Let's get you back to
detention.

